'''彼得·罗伯特·拉蒙特·布朗'''（{{lang-en|Peter Robert Lamont Brown}}，{{bd|1935年|7月26日|}}）是[[英国|英国]]的[[历史学家|历史学家]]，专攻[[古典时代晚期|古典时代晚期]]和中世纪早期的历史，现为[[普林斯顿大学|普林斯顿大学]]历史系[[榮譽退休|榮譽退休]]教授<ref>{{Cite web|title=Peter Brown {{!}} Department of History|url=http://history.princeton.edu/people/peter-brown|website=history.princeton.edu|access-date=2016-01-31|archive-date=2022-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220605180846/https://history.princeton.edu/people/peter-brown}} Ruby Shao, "Peter Brown: Inventor of late antiquity", ''The Daily Princetonian'', Apr. 20, 2017: http://www.dailyprincetonian.com/article/2017/04/peter-brown-late-antiquity {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailyprincetonian.com/article/2017/04/peter-brown-late-antiquity |date=20211213162717 }}.</ref>，獲誉“古代晚期研究领域的发明者”<ref>[https://www.princeton.edu/history/people/display_person.xml?netid=prbrown Faculty Page] {{Wayback|url=https://www.princeton.edu/history/people/display_person.xml?netid=prbrown |date=20150924104955 }} at Princeton University. See also [http://www.amphilsoc.org/memhist/search?creator=Peter+Brown&title=&subject=4.+Humanities&subdiv=404&mem=Resident&year=1995&year-max=1995&dead=Alive&keyword=&smode=advanced American Philosophical Society record.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233042/http://www.amphilsoc.org/memhist/search?creator=Peter+Brown&title=&subject=4.+Humanities&subdiv=404&mem=Resident&year=1995&year-max=1995&dead=Alive&keyword=&smode=advanced |date=3 March 2016 }}</ref>，主要作品有《古代晚期的世界》（''The World of Late Antiquity''）、《希波的奥古斯丁》（''Augustine of Hippo: A Biography''）等。

